{"tid":417793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"賊仔趁磁磚舖冇人 潛入擸走數十元","createTime":"2017-09-29T04:13:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-29T07:55:23.000Z","uid":122,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f36b0e62cad9a792498206ef4354fec2bf1bc908","tid":417793,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T04:13:58.000Z","msg":"<strong>賊仔趁磁磚舖冇人 潛入擸走數十元</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170929/large/1506655778_0d14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170929%2Flarge%2F1506655778_0d14.jpg&h=c5ec0bff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n旺角亞皆老街35A號一間磁磚專賣店，今早10時22分，職員外出一會後返回店舖，發現店內有搜掠痕迹，懷疑遭人爆竊，於是報警。警員到場調查，未發現店內有被撬毀痕迹，相信有竊匪趁職員外出期間，潛入舖內，掠去數十元散銀後逃去。"},{"pid":"f3c2bc37ad8c50e6191258b6fb0636ba5c9d2fb3","tid":417793,"uid":97708,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T04:15:31.000Z","msg":"咁撚大筆錢 個賊冇性架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c91c18ace2ac0b51f7bdb1c0740c6cf2b0a6ef","tid":417793,"uid":55043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T04:16:56.000Z","msg":"市道咁差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8916188d73da6a198c80be857e6da4287fbe9277","tid":417793,"uid":69522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T04:23:31.000Z","msg":"保險賠幾多？"},{"pid":"76ad049bf039d4e27aacf8924455921d40c41eb8","tid":417793,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T04:24:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a3c0dcfcaa6da4d7063bf5e46983448fac8b77a","tid":417793,"uid":58791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T04:25:30.000Z","msg":"肯定係老同無錢周圍括<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35c316105283d71014ec4952a7a3685963293600","tid":417793,"uid":50554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"